# Agent self-continue (CEO loop)

Cloud agents **stop after one reply**. Use this loop so work continues across runs.

## Every orchestrated session

1. `MISSION=$(python3 -m shorts_bot.agent_ops mission new --name "…")`
2. Log every dispatch: `agent_ops log --mission $MISSION …`
3. Before ending: `python3 -m shorts_bot.agent_ops mission continue --mission $MISSION`

## When blocked (login, SMS, CAPTCHA)

```bash
python3 -m shorts_bot.owner_ping "Plain English — what you need"
```

Do **not** idle waiting for owner if ping channel works.

